measurements_data.comments: Today, we have complete control over MSW waste from all governorates in Oman, and we measure all waste quantities received, resulting in data that is more accurate. As a result, waste quantities 10 years ago may not accurately reflect Oman's status at the time. Furthermore, other factors such as population growth, urbanization, and economic development should be considered.
